title: use Linux-, not Windows-style, line terminators
pid: 214c56b0-03f1-4709-9bc9-2ec6f742fa16
body: |2-
  Avoid that by specifying the terminator explicitly:
  w = csv.writer( csvfile, delimiter=',', quotechar = '\"',
                  lineterminator="\n",
                  quoting = csv.QUOTE_MINIMAL)
misc:
- Had_ID_Before_Import
